room_title: Escape room "Dark Carnival" by Enigma Puzzle House in Bloomington (IN)
review: Went here with a group of friends for my birthday, and it was so much fun! We did Dark Carnival and it was the perfect level of challenge for our six person group. The owner was super accommodating and kind, too! We're definitely going back for the new rooms when they open!

room_title: Escape room "Dark Carnival" by Enigma Puzzle House in Bloomington (IN)
